Uses of Package
org.omancode.r.ui

Packages that use org.omancode.r.ui
org.omancode.r.ui R user interface elements including: A Swing console with a command history. A JTree representing objects in the R environment. A interface for UIs that gather input from the user and execute an R command.  
 

Classes in org.omancode.r.ui used by org.omancode.r.ui
RObjectNode
          Tree node that represents an object in R.
RObjectTreeBuilder
          Builds a JTree that represents the objects in an R environment.
